			// | End   | Tab    | Tab   | Q    | W   | E   | R   | T   | Y     | T      | Y   | U   | I   | O   | P    | [     | ]     | \      |
			// | Pg Up | Caps   | Ctrl  | A    | S   | D   | F   | G   | H     | G      | H   | J   | K   | L   | ;    | '     | Enter | Enter  |
			// | Pg Dn | Up     | Shift | Z    | X   | C   | V   | B   | N     | B      | N   | M   | ,   | .   | /    | Shift | Up    |        |
			// | Left  | Dn     | Right | Ctrl | Alt | Win | Spc | Spc | Enter | Bk Spc | Spc | Spc | Win | Alt | Ctrl | Left  | Dn    | Right  |
			bindings = <
			&kp GRAVE  &kp ESC    &kp N1     &kp N2     &kp N3     &kp N4     &kp N5     &trans     &trans     &kp N6     &kp N7     &kp N8     &kp N9     &kp N0     &kp BSPC   &kp DEL    &trans     &trans       
			&kp HOME   &kp TAB    &kp Q      &kp W      &kp E      &kp R      &kp T      &trans     &trans     &kp Y      &kp U      &kp I      &kp O      &kp P      &kp MINUS  &kp EQUAL  &trans     &trans       
